{"tid":2194052,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"今何在既《悟空傳》算唔算係網絡文學入面最有深度既一篇","createTime":"2020-09-08T09:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T13:54:05.000Z","uid":343520,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a491eefdb3792c667896ba0af7f89e89932fbe9d","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"寫作手法雖然輕鬆搞笑，但係融入左佛學思想，反思人生意義<br />\n<br />\n無論故事既結構、懸念既設計都係頂級水平<br />\n<br />\n睇完對人生真係會有一種唔同既感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來一生一世那麼短暫，原來當你發現所愛的，就應該不顧一切的去追求。因為生命隨時都會終止，命運是大海，當你能夠暢遊時，你就要盡情游向你的所愛，因為你不知道狂流什麼時候會到來，捲走一切希望與夢想。<br />\n<br />\n                                         &mdash;&mdash;今何在《悟空傳》"},{"pid":"52a0821fb6cc81f4a5858405dc1a354cf7456e05","tid":2194052,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a1b7cac2f070e770c26424a90fa1169f0c42e5","tid":2194052,"uid":156144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"特拉福買家俱樂部"},{"pid":"52455cab97ef4a9523974774838b2806d9397c13","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"81a1b7cac2f070e770c26424a90fa1169f0c42e5","tid":2194052,"uid":156144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"特拉福買家俱樂部"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:31:51.000Z","msg":"你講乜？"},{"pid":"8661bc67a4333c988bf51ccdc60ebdb85ae3dc3d","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:45:02.000Z","msg":"為什麼要讓一個已無作為的人去看他年少時的理想？<br />\n&mdash;&mdash; 今何在 《悟空傳》"},{"pid":"a23441a09ec41126c07957e500619a80ec3bf023","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:46:37.000Z","msg":"死就是甚麼也看不見，甚麼也聽不見，甚麼也感覺不到，甚麼也不會想&mdash;&mdash;就像你未出生時一樣。"},{"pid":"bbf386dba70c715e9f892c4c916f1876da72b032","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:50:57.000Z","msg":"生難道又不是夢幻麼？你所得的你最終全會失去，你認為那是真的，你就會痛苦，而你知道那不過是一個遊戲一個夢境，你就能解脫。人生在世，百年也好，千萬年也好，都是未來前的一瞬，這一瞬後你什麼都沒有，你曾有的只有你的自己。你在世上永遠地孤寂著，永遠找不到能依託你的東西，除非你放棄你自己，融入到造物之中，成為萬重宇宙一點塵埃，你就安樂了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e230d74c4bd38b658f68ca8d411f58997e983435","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:16:45.000Z","msg":"連登冇人睇好文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b84ccb2bdb0d1e066b28c4bdd8af33a389dad7e","tid":2194052,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"生我何用 不能歡笑<br />\n滅我何用 不減狂驕"},{"pid":"5e017e98d2c3174f5f0257fb5aaabf112d45f302","tid":2194052,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81a1b7cac2f070e770c26424a90fa1169f0c42e5","tid":2194052,"uid":156144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"特拉福買家俱樂部"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:31:08.000Z","msg":"藥命俱樂部"},{"pid":"7d6ebb77397eb3faee25e99628d6c9f1f178204b","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0b84ccb2bdb0d1e066b28c4bdd8af33a389dad7e","tid":2194052,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:20:24.000Z","msg":"生我何用 不能歡笑<br />\n滅我何用 不減狂驕"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:31:35.000Z","msg":"就咁睇可能有少少中二病 <br />\n但如果代入左個故事世界就唔會咁覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f3b2c282c81fce448ca2075d57bb6c665a8a43","tid":2194052,"uid":41813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"你是從石頭中蹦出來的吧？你總是憂慮，因為幾萬年來沉寂的你還在害怕著那林間飛速的跳躍，千百萬撲面而來的事物，而你知道你能如此自由地掌握自己的時間是極為短暫的，你能感受到自己這樣自由思考的時間是極短暫的，為了這短暫的時光，你要盡力地去抓住你所遇見的。要知道你生命中所出現的，都是在你漫長的時光中來到你面前的，去珍惜它們吧，孩子。"},{"pid":"2f0d35bf5439984c96050c7121966de9313eb28f","tid":2194052,"uid":41353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"105e9796879960c6ca9b52c55481658c77c8df61","tid":2194052,"uid":67428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"佢好似係大陸小說...<br />\n唔理好睇定唔好睇，麻煩入番大陸小說po自己推"},{"pid":"3a64d45e13fada9fe090d14543ae47b4f3649cfc","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"105e9796879960c6ca9b52c55481658c77c8df61","tid":2194052,"uid":67428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"佢好似係大陸小說...<br />\n唔理好睇定唔好睇，麻煩入番大陸小說po自己推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"我想出黎開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5255b9655084362ed73ceda51b8e0554fad22c7","tid":2194052,"uid":66274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T12:11:55.000Z","msg":"短而精<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好憎依家啲作者水蛇春咁長，好悶"},{"pid":"32b56b364b4c7617d8a74b834684979d3fb5f0fd","tid":2194052,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"有些人為了不再失去，而失去了所有。"}]}